Package: isdmtools
Type: Package
Title: Toolkit for Facilitating Integrated Species Distribution Modeling
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Akoeugnigan Idelphonse",
                 family = "SODE",
                 role = c("cre", "aut"),
                 email = "sdidelphonse@gmail.com",
                 comment = "Maintainer of the package")
Date: 2025-09-08
Maintainer: <sdidelphonse@gmail.com>
Description: A suite of tools for for manipulating and visualising spatial data, as well as for block cross-validation and evaluating spatial models with multisource point datasets. 
    These tools are designed to assist with building and analyzing Integrated Species Distribution Models (ISDMs) with a focus on the Bayesian framework.
URL: https://github.com/sodeidelphonse/isdmtools
BugReports: https://github.com/sodeidelphonse/isdmtools/issues
